Found it! The issue is in `session.dmScope`:

```json
"session": {
  "dmScope": "per-channel-peer",
  "reset": {
    "mode": "daily",
    "atHour": 7
  }
}
```

**Current:** `per-channel-peer` = each channel+peer combination gets its own session  
**You want:** All DMs from all channels going to the main session
